<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#111;line-height:1.3;">
  {{ notification.title | e }}
</h2>

<p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;">
  {{ notification.body | e }}
</p>

{% if notification.meta.requester_email %}
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin:0 0 20px;background:#f9fafb;border-radius:6px;width:100%;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;">
      Requested by
    </td>
    <td style="padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#111;font-family:ui-monospace,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;text-align:right;">
      {{ notification.meta.requester_email | e }}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
{% endif %}

<p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;">
  What this is
</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;">
  An in-app member clicked &ldquo;Request admin access&rdquo; from their
  dashboard.  Admin gives them CameraNode management, MCP API key
  generation, recording-policy control, and audit-log access &mdash;
  the programmatic + write-capable privileges.
</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;">
  How to act
</p>
<ol style="margin:0 0 24px;padding-left:20px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#374151;">
  <li>Open Settings (link below) and review your member list</li>
  <li>If approving, promote the requester to admin via Clerk &mdash;
      the change propagates to their JWT within ~60 seconds</li>
  <li>If declining, no action needed.  The request stays in the
      audit log; the requester won't be notified directly</li>
  <li>If you don't recognize the requester, audit recent invitations
      <strong>before</strong> deciding</li>
</ol>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
  <tr>
    <td style="background:#22c55e;border-radius:6px;">
      <a href="{{ dashboard_url }}/settings"
         style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 18px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#0a0a0f;text-decoration:none;">
        Open Settings &rarr;
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin:24px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.5;">
  This alert went only to organization admins.
</p>
